  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "PostgreSQL DBA (Senior)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><p>We are looking for a Senior PostgreSQL DBA to build, maintain, and optimize high-availability database\nenvironments. The candidate will be responsible for daily database operations, monitoring, automation, security, and performance tuning, ensuring the reliability and integrity of our database systems.</p><p><strong>Key Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Build and maintain new high-availability (HA) database environments, including monitoring systems, automation systems, backup systems, and log systems.</li><li>Perform daily PostgreSQL and MySQL database monitoring, maintenance, optimization, and troubleshooting.</li><li>Ensure database security and hardening to protect data integrity and maintain backup availability.</li><li>Participate in database cutovers, including master-slave switchover, BI data push, cluster data synchronization, and data migration.</li><li>Conduct stress testing and performance optimization for production databases.</li><li>Set up database clusters and disaster recovery environments to achieve high availability.</li><li>Provide technical support and guidance to team members and collaborate effectively within the team.</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li>Bachelor’s Degree, Post-Graduate Diploma, or Professional Degree in Computer Science, Information Technology, or equivalent.</li></ul><ul><li>Minimum 3 years of experience as a PostgreSQL DBA or in a similar senior database role.</li></ul><ul><li>Strong knowledge and hands-on experience with:  PostgreSQL database administration; Database monitoring and automation system; High-availability database setups and disaster recovery; SQL performance tuning,  optimization, and troubleshooting application issues; Database security and access control; Production database testing and stress testing</li></ul><ul><li>Familiarity with MySQL is a plus.</li></ul><ul><li>Strong team player with the ability to work independently.</li></ul><p><strong>Company Benefits</strong></p><ul><li>Attractive rewards for long-term service staff</li><li>Friendly and energetic working environment, including flexible working hours and staff birthday celebrations</li><li>Medical insurance coverage</li></ul>",
